<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA81">
<l>āḷamar veṉṟi yaṭukaḷattu ḷaññāṉṟu</l>
<l>vāḷamar vēṇṭi varainaṭṭu – nīḷaravaic</l>
<l>cuṟṟik kaṭaintāṉ peyaraṉṟē toṉṉarakaip</l>
<l>paṟṟik kaṭattum paṭai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The name of him, isn’t it, who churned by setting up the mountain,</l>
<l>coiling [around it] the long snake, wanting a fight for glory</l>
<l>that day on the victorious battle field abounding in men,</l>
<l>is the weapon that grips [and] drives away old hell.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
